My visual data story about student have piercing in uni

Angelina Yu

What’s going on with this data?

this data is for me to observe how many student at uni have piercings, because i am a piercing lover. I spent a week observing the students’ piercings and recorded what types of piercings they had and how many piercings they had.

gender of piercing

this plot is for me to observe how many male and female have piercing, What is the ratio of male and female piercings type.

#distribution of number of piercings: nose vs others

this plot is for me to observe how many people have nose piercings and compare to others, i can see most of the student have 2 nose stud.

#how many student with piercings are seen on each day from this plot i can see that students wearing piercings for a week. and most student like to wear on piercing each day, and The most students take piercings on Friday. and on Saterday there were the only day that has student wear 4 piercings.
